start.label: i have to love you and leave you

examples.en: A puppy is naturally affectionate and excitable.
She was by nature a very affectionate person.
I rest your affectionate sister, E.
Jo is very affectionate towards her.
He is the most affectionate and cuddly dog I have ever known.
He's very loving and affectionate with his sister.
Marjorie gave his hair an affectionate tweak.
